---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="회사소개 페이지 | 피키픽 | 포토부스 대여 및 기업 행사 렌탈 전문"
  description="피키픽 포토부스는 브랜드 팝업스토어, 기업 행사, 웨딩, 파티 등 다양한 이벤트에 맞춤형 포토부스 렌탈 서비스를 제공합니다. PICKYPIC PHOTOBOOTH 회사소개."
>
  <!-- Hero Carousel -->
  <section class="about-hero" aria-label="회사소개 히어로 이미지">
    <!-- Desktop -->
    <div class="about-hero-desktop">
      <img
        src="/images/company/company-hero.jpg"
        alt="피키픽 포토부스 회사소개"
        loading="eager"
        width="1920"
        height="1056"
      />
    </div>
    <!-- Mobile -->
    <div class="about-hero-mobile">
      <img
        src="/images/company/company-hero-mo.jpg"
        alt="피키픽 포토부스 회사소개"
        loading="eager"
        width="750"
        height="750"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Introduction -->
  <article class="about-content">
    <section class="about-intro gs-fade-up">
      <h1 class="about-heading">PICKYPIC PHOTOBOOTH<sup>&reg;</sup></h1>
      <p class="about-description">
        It is not enough that we build products that function, that are understandable and usable,
        we also need to build products that bring joy and excitement, pleasure and fun, and, yes,
        beauty to idiosyncratic question, the answer he gives will necessarily be unique as well.
      </p>
      <nav class="about-buttons" aria-label="회사 관련 링크">
        <a href="#" class="about-btn" download>회사소개</a>
        <a href="/products" class="about-btn">제품소개</a>
        <a href="mailto:pickypic.marketing@gmail.com" class="about-btn">협업제안</a>
      </nav>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-hero-desktop {
    display: block;
  }

  .about-hero-mobile {
    display: none;
  }

  .about-hero img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero-desktop {
      display: none;
    }
    .about-hero-mobile {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  /* Content */
  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 100px 24px 120px;
  }

  .about-intro {
    max-width: 720px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }

  .about-heading sup {
    font-size: 16px;
    vertical-align: super;
  }

  .about-description {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #6e6e73;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    word-break: keep-all;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .about-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 18px 60px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    border: 1px solid #a2a2a2;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .about-btn:hover {
    background: #000000;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      padding: 60px 20px 80px;
    }

    .about-heading {
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .about-heading sup {
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .about-description {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .about-buttons {
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .about-btn {
      padding: 12px 32px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
</style>
